        <section name="What is Hippo Site Toolkit 2?">
            
            <span class='shortdesc'>
                Hippo Site Toolkit 2 is being finalized for release mid-April. The documentation
                will be online at the time of the release. In the meantime, you can already
                check out the <a href="apidocs/index.html">API documentation</a>.
            </span>

            <p> 
                Hippo ECM comes with a set of tools and components to allow rapid development of websites, the Hippo Site Toolkit 2. 
            </p>

            <p> 
                Hippo Site Toolkit 2 is an open source toolkit for Java web developers, to build websites based on <span
                    class="expire_event">sitename change</span><a href="http://docs.onehippo.org/hippo-ecm">Hippo CMS 7</a>. Assemble your
                website by configuring templates, site map, navigation and URL space through a straightforward user interface, that
                integrates with Hippo CMS. Create a JSP based view layer using the provided tag library and expression language. 
            </p>
            
